Sergio Aguero scored his 100th goal for Manchester City against Manchester United on Sunday . 
  Manuel Pellegrini is facing the sack after the derby defeat at Old Trafford . 
  Manchester City are in need of a summer overhaul and could target Paul Pogba and Raheem Sterling . 
  Aguero has scored 100 goals in 158 appearances for the club . 
  The Argentine scored the goal that won the Premier League in 2012 . 
 